#3 binary distribution
before understanding binary distribution first we need to learn environment variables in an operating system

What are environment variables, how are these used?
The environment variables are the placeholders we can at operating system to store values and can be used across the application programs we run on the system.

	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	


























































	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	

	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	























